kin","tag-poverty-faqr","tag-provision-al-rizq","tag-weakness-al-daf","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4WU","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/16\/work-rizq-like-birds\/","url_meta":{"origin":19028,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Reliance: Must work for provision like the birds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you were to rely upon Allah with reliance due to Him, He would provide for you just as He provides for the birds. They go out in the morning with empty stomachs and return\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36965,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/22\/best-provision-taqwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":19028,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Taqwa: Best provision for travel is fear of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I intend to travel, so supplicate for my provision.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cMay Allah provide you with fear of Him.\u201d The man said, \u201cGive me more.\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26334,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/13\/dua-complain-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19028,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Whoever complains to Allah, relief will come","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is afflicted by a pressing need and complains to people, his need will never be satisfied. Whoever is afflicted by a pressing need and complains to Allah, eventually Allah will provide for him, sooner\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11322,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/10\/hiyat-al-dunya-almost-worthless\/","url_meta":{"origin":19028,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Worldly life is nearly worthless to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the world were as worthy to Allah as the wing of a mosquito, an unbeliever would not even be given a sip of water.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2320 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26054,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/12\/blessed-content-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":19028,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Contentment: Blessed is one satisfied with Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 12, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn 'Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed is one who is guided to Islam, whose livelihood is sufficient, and who is content with what he has.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2349 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39937,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/25\/hand-of-allah-united\/","url_meta":{"origin":19028,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jama\u2019ah: Hand of Allah with Muslims united on truth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 25, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hand of Allah is with the united community.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2166 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u200c\u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \